Designed the /w/ protocol. Replaced /events/ and /fastevent/ with unified POST /w/{namespace}/{verb}. The ? is the routing signal: present = CloudFront Function returns 202 (data in URL, always captured, free), absent = forward to Lambda (body, might 503). Namespace = plugin = repo. IAM scopes each Lambda to its own S3 prefix. Teams deploy independently with their own process. Contract is files at URLs. Updated platform spec, events-endpoint spec, cf-short-urls.js, build script, and comments schema (collapsed two operations into one).
